He ain't ready for a laser 
experiment just yet!

405
00:25:08,530 --> 00:25:10,360
Damn right!

406
00:25:10,360 --> 00:25:13,320
How much does he think one seraphim costs?!

407
00:25:13,320 --> 00:25:16,040
Should I rip this numbskull's head off?!

408
00:25:16,040 --> 00:25:17,200
That's evil!

409
00:25:17,580 --> 00:25:19,870
Don't show pirates even a lick of mercy!

410
00:25:21,460 --> 00:25:23,460
I'm gonna bury them right here!

411
00:25:23,460 --> 00:25:25,210
That's really evil!

412
00:25:25,210 --> 00:25:28,300
S-Shark, beat the devil outta them!

413
00:25:28,300 --> 00:25:30,220
Give 'em a good thrashing!

414
00:25:30,220 --> 00:25:31,840
That's enough!

415
00:25:31,840 --> 00:25:34,300
I wasn't gonna go that far!

416
00:25:34,300 --> 00:25:38,390
Eureka! I just came up with a new invention!

417
00:25:38,390 --> 00:25:40,020
Really now?

418
00:25:40,020 --> 00:25:42,270
I'll take care of this, then!

419
00:25:42,270 --> 00:25:43,770
I'll leave the rest to you...

