Another one?!

897
00:30:10,500 --> 00:30:12,250
What's with you guys?!

898
00:30:12,830 --> 00:30:15,170
You must be the Straw Hat Pirates.

899
00:30:15,170 --> 00:30:17,630
We are! Now tell us what's
wrong with these shoes!

900
00:30:17,630 --> 00:30:19,590
They're stuck to the floor!

901
00:30:19,590 --> 00:30:23,590
Dom shoes can easily be controlled
by the magnets in the laboratory.

902
00:30:23,970 --> 00:30:25,800
So resistance is futile, then.

903
00:30:26,430 --> 00:30:28,930
We can't trust pirates.

904
00:30:28,930 --> 00:30:33,770
There was also a female Vegapunk,
and another that was talking over the speakers...

905
00:30:33,770 --> 00:30:34,810
Yeah...

906
00:30:34,810 --> 00:30:36,860
I am Vegapunk as well.

907
00:30:36,860 --> 00:30:38,730
I don't get it!

908
00:30:38,730 --> 00:30:40,740
How many of you guys are there?!

909
00:30:41,240 --> 00:30:42,490
Maybe I'm Vegapunk, too...

910
00:30:42,490 --> 00:30:43,490
What?!

911
00:30:43,490 --> 00:30:46,240
Like hell you are!

912
00:30:50,660 --> 00:30:54,370
Does this island look like
the future to all of you?

913
00:30:54,370 --> 00:30:56,880
Yeah, it's amazing!

914
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:58,380
It's not just any future!

915
00:30:58,380 --> 00:31:00,460
There were those mechanical sea beasts!

916
00:31:01,130 --> 00:31:04,880
Plus, the Vegaforce-01
and the island A.C. system, too!

917
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:06,930
It's a hell of a future!

918
00:31:06,930 --> 00:31:09,890
And I've never seen a city like that...

919
00:31:09,890 --> 00:31:14,890
I wanna snoop around
and see how everything works!

920
00:31:14,890 --> 00:31:16,650
Don't be so cold!

921
00:31:16,650 --> 00:31:19,860
Let's be pals, Vega!

922
00:31:20,650 --> 00:31:22,940
Even my technology is still so far behind...

923
00:31:25,950 --> 00:31:27,620
This island is from the past.

924
00:31:28,620 --> 00:31:29,870
What?!

925
00:31:30,410 --> 00:31:32,250
What do you mean "from the past"?!

926
00:31:32,660 --> 00:31:35,460
What if I were to tell you...

927
00:31:36,080 --> 00:31:41,710
that 900 years ago, there was
an advanced kingdom like Egghead...?

928
00:31:41,710 --> 00:31:43,340
Would you believe me?

929
00:31:44,970 --> 00:31:46,880
Nine hundred years ago?!

930
00:31:46,880 --> 00:31:48,850
What are you talking about?!

931
00:31:54,180 --> 00:31:55,810
It's real!

932
00:31:55,810 --> 00:31:57,440
Look, Chopper!

933
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:59,690
It's not a holo-holo!

934
00:32:00,020 --> 00:32:01,440
It's really there!

935
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:02,690
It's made of iron!

936
00:32:05,700 --> 00:32:07,110
What is this?!

937
00:32:07,110 --> 00:32:08,660
It's pretty beat-up.

938
00:32:09,410 --> 00:32:11,370
Did it use to work?

939
00:32:11,870 --> 00:32:15,000
That would require futuristic technology.

940
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:16,830
Isn't it too old?

941
00:32:16,830 --> 00:32:18,580
I wanna ride it!

942
00:32:18,580 --> 00:32:20,590
Yeah, let's do it!

943
00:32:20,590 --> 00:32:22,340
Let's go, Chopper!
